{"type": "article", "id": 4128, "title": "Alessi 果盘", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-05T08:25:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052330535lyZTgraBtC2m4QX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利家居设计品牌 Alessi 今年邀请来自巴黎的女性建筑师 Odile Decq 设计了一款果盘，名为「Twist Again」。运动一直是 Odile Decq 为 Alessi 设计产品的关键词，她总是擅于用一些很小的元素呈现自己的设计特点，这款果盘也是，选用了金属板材作为原材料，将其剪切与折叠，生成一个动态的漩涡造型，给人流畅的视觉体验。定价 57.8 欧元（约合人民币 438 元），<a href=\"http://www.questodesign.com/kitchen-and-tabletop/kitchen-tabletop/bowls-baskets/alessi-twist-again-fruit-holder.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233051G3s0TE8HpZYbKwCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233052TrDGxMAipb7OB0fZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233052XyVEmcjzHfantU3D.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}